<Layout::Text text-l text-f>
	<h3>Example usage</h3>
	<p>To display the current command-line tool version, along with the platform and architecture, in a terminal run the <Ascua::Prism::Inline @language="shell" @code="surreal start" /> command with the required arguments.</p>
	<codes vertical>
		<Code @name="docs-cli-start-main.shell" text="Command line">
			user@localhost % surreal start --log trace --user root --pass root memory
		</Code>
		<Code @name="docs/cli/start/main.txt" />
	</codes>
</Layout::Text>

